        <odd id="ref7">
            <head>General note</head>
            <p>The collection has also been described by Joseph Ewan, "Fougeroux de Bondaroy (1732-1789) and his Projected Revision of Duhamel du Monceau's "Traité" (1755) on Trees and Shrubs. I. An Analytical Guide to Persons, Gardens, and Works mentioned in the Manuscripts," American Philosophical Society Proceedings 103 (1959): 807-818.</p>
        </odd>
