        </odd>
        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Henry Louis Duhamel du Monceau was a French agronomist and botanist; Auguste Denis Fougeroux de Bondaroy was his nephew and heir.</p>
        </bioghist>
